            "title": "Galan Lithium secures A$40M to support project expansion",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li><span>Galan Lithium (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLNLF\" title=\"Galan Lithium Limited\">GLNLF</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20380254-a-40-million-institutional-placement-to-support-30-percent-expansion-of-phase-1-hombre-muerto\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"secured\">secured</a> A$40 million in commitments from institutional and sophisticated investors, including major shareholder Clean Elements Fund, via a placement at A$0.41 per share.</span></li>\n<li>\n<span>The </span>directors have separately committed to subscribe for an additional A$1M subject to shareholder approval.</li>\n<li><span>The institutional placement involves two tranches: Tranche 1 (~86.6M shares) settles in early February 2026, while Tranche 2 (13.4M shares, including director participation)</span></li>\n<li>The proceeds will be used to expand production at HMW from the currently planned 4 ktpa LCE to 5.2 ktpa LCE, fund exploration activities at Greenbushes South, and provide working capital.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
