            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>37 Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HHHEF\" title=\"37 Capital Inc.\">HHHEF</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20380270-37-capital-announces-non-brokered-private-placement-financing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"proposed\">proposed</a> a non-brokered private placement to raise up to $250,000 by the issuance of up to 2.5M units of the company at a price of $0.10 per unit.</li>\n<li>Each unit will consist of one common share of the company and one share purchase warrant to acquire one common share of the company at a price of $0.15 per share for a period of 3 years.</li>\n<li>The funds raised from the financing will be used towards general working capital.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
